# EscapeZoom Financial Logic (theory only)

## 1. Configuration Layers
- **Global:** Tax rate, default commission.
- **Overrides:** More specific levels (game, city, type, or combination) exist and participate in priority.

## 2. Commission Rate Priority (Waterfall)
1) Game-specific → 2) City + game type → 3) City only → 4) Game type only → 5) Global default. First available wins.

## 3. Payment Models
- **Full payment:** Base = total after owner discounts; commission and tax on base; owner share = base − (commission + tax); platform discounts do not reduce owner share.
- **Prepayment:** Commission/tax on full booking total; owner share = deposit − (commission + tax); if commission+tax > deposit, owner share is negative.

## 4. Discount Impact
- **Owner discounts:** Reduce base for commission/tax.
- **Platform discounts:** Do not reduce owner share; they are platform cost only.

## 5. Credit Gateways
- Full payment only; no prepayment.
- No coupon or loyalty discount; only owner discounts.
- Settlement requires manual admin approval before wallet credit.

## 6. Settlement Timing
- **Standard orders:** Auto wallet credit after fixed delay (e.g. 24h) from slot start.
- **Credit orders:** Same delay but release only after admin approval.

## 7. Affiliate
- Orders can be linked to affiliate.
- Affiliate commission is separate from owner share.
- Affiliate reporting and settlement are separate.
